---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '@/data/site';

const title = 'Terms of Use';
const description =
  'Terms of Use for TopBestLLCService.com. Read the terms governing your use of our website, content, and services.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="bg-gray-50 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Terms of Use</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-500">
          Last updated: {siteConfig.lastUpdated}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 sm:py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:text-gray-900 prose-p:text-gray-700 prose-a:text-teal-700 prose-a:underline-offset-2 hover:prose-a:text-teal-900">

      <p>
        Welcome to {siteConfig.name} (<a href={siteConfig.url}>{siteConfig.url}</a>). By accessing or using this website, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use this website.
      </p>
      <p>
        This website is operated by {siteConfig.operator} ("we," "us," or "our").
      </p>

      <!-- Nature of Content -->
      <h2 id="nature-of-content">1. Nature of Content</h2>

      <h3>Informational Purposes Only</h3>
      <p>
        The content on {siteConfig.name} is provided for general informational and educational purposes only. Nothing on this website constitutes legal, tax, financial, or professional advice. You should consult with qualified professionals before making any business or legal decisions, including decisions regarding LLC formation.
      </p>

      <h3>No Attorney-Client Relationship</h3>
      <p>
        Using this website does not create an attorney-client relationship, a fiduciary relationship, or any professional advisory relationship between you and {siteConfig.operator} or any contributor to this website.
      </p>

      <h3>Accuracy of Information</h3>
      <p>
        While we strive to provide accurate, up-to-date information, we make no warranties or guarantees regarding the accuracy, completeness, timeliness, or reliability of any content on this website. State filing requirements, fees, service provider pricing, and features may change at any time. Always verify critical information directly with the relevant state agency or service provider.
      </p>

      <!-- AI-Generated Content and Editorial Personas -->
      <h2 id="content-creation">2. Content Creation Disclosure</h2>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50/50 p-6 not-prose my-6">
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">Important Transparency Notice:</strong> We believe in full transparency about how our content is created. Please read this section carefully.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h3>Use of Artificial Intelligence</h3>
      <p>
        Some content on this website may be created, drafted, or assisted by artificial intelligence (AI) tools. AI-generated or AI-assisted content is reviewed and edited by our editorial team for accuracy and quality before publication. However, despite our review process, AI-generated content may occasionally contain errors, inaccuracies, or outdated information. We encourage you to verify any critical information independently.
      </p>

      <h3>Editorial Personas and Pseudonyms</h3>
      <p>
        Some author names, biographies, and team member profiles appearing on this website may be pseudonyms, pen names, or fictitious editorial personas. These personas are used for editorial and branding purposes and do not necessarily represent specific real individuals. The use of editorial personas does not diminish our commitment to content accuracy; all content, regardless of the attributed author, undergoes our standard editorial review process.
      </p>

      <h3>User Reviews and Testimonials</h3>
      <p>
        Any reviews, testimonials, or user experiences presented on this website may be edited for clarity, length, or grammar. Some may be representative composites rather than verbatim quotes from individual users. We do not guarantee that any specific user experience will be typical or representative of the results you may achieve.
      </p>

      <!-- Affiliate Relationships -->
      <h2 id="affiliate-relationships">3. Affiliate Relationships</h2>
      <p>
        {siteConfig.name} participates in affiliate marketing programs. When you click on certain links on our website and make a purchase, we may receive a commission from the service provider at no additional cost to you. Affiliate compensation may influence which services appear on our site, the order in which they are presented, and the prominence of their placement.
      </p>
      <p>
        For full details about our affiliate relationships and how they affect our content, please review our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.
      </p>

      <!-- Intellectual Property -->
      <h2 id="intellectual-property">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        All content on this website — including text, graphics, logos, icons, images, data compilations, and software — is the property of {siteConfig.operator} or its content suppliers and is protected by applicable copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws.
      </p>
      <p>
        You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, create derivative works from, publicly display, or commercially exploit any content from this website without our prior written consent, except for limited personal, non-commercial use (such as printing a single article for your own reference).
      </p>

      <!-- Third-Party Links -->
      <h2 id="third-party-links">5. Third-Party Links and Services</h2>
      <p>
        This website contains links to third-party websites, including those of LLC formation service providers. These links are provided for your convenience and informational purposes. We do not control, endorse, or assume responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party website.
      </p>
      <p>
        When you click a link to a third-party website, you leave {siteConfig.name} and become subject to that website's terms of use and privacy policy. We are not responsible for any transactions, interactions, or disputes between you and any third-party service provider.
      </p>

      <!-- Limitation of Liability -->
      <h2 id="limitation-of-liability">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, {siteConfig.operator} and its officers, directors, employees, agents, and affiliates shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or related to your use of (or inability to use) this website, including but not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Errors or inaccuracies in content</li>
        <li>Personal injury or property damage resulting from your use of the website</li>
        <li>Unauthorized access to your personal information</li>
        <li>Loss of data, profits, or business opportunities</li>
        <li>Decisions made based on content found on this website</li>
        <li>Interactions with third-party service providers linked from this website</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Disclaimers -->
      <h2 id="disclaimers">7. Disclaimers</h2>
      <p>
        This website is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We disclaim all warranties, including but not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement</li>
        <li>Warranties that the website will be uninterrupted, secure, or error-free</li>
        <li>Warranties regarding the accuracy, reliability, or completeness of any content</li>
        <li>Warranties that any errors will be corrected</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- User Conduct -->
      <h2 id="user-conduct">8. User Conduct</h2>
      <p>
        By using this website, you agree not to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the website for any unlawful purpose</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the website or its systems</li>
        <li>Transmit any viruses, malware, or harmful code</li>
        <li>Scrape, crawl, or use automated tools to extract content without our permission</li>
        <li>Impersonate any person or entity or misrepresent your affiliation</li>
        <li>Interfere with or disrupt the website's operation</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Indemnification -->
      <h2 id="indemnification">9. Indemnification</h2>
      <p>
        You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless {siteConfig.operator}, its officers, directors, employees, and agents from and against any claims, liabilities, damages, losses, costs, or expenses (including reasonable attorneys' fees) arising out of or related to your use of this website, your violation of these Terms of Use, or your violation of any rights of a third party.
      </p>

      <!-- Governing Law -->
      <h2 id="governing-law">10. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms of Use shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable law, without regard to conflict of law principles. Any disputes arising from or related to these Terms of Use or your use of this website shall be resolved through the appropriate legal channels in the jurisdiction of {siteConfig.operator}'s registered office.
      </p>

      <!-- Changes -->
      <h2 id="changes">11. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Use at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to this page. The "last updated" date at the top of this page indicates when these terms were most recently revised. Your continued use of the website after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated terms.
      </p>

      <!-- Severability -->
      <h2 id="severability">12. Severability</h2>
      <p>
        If any provision of these Terms of Use is found to be unenforceable or invalid, that provision shall be limited or eliminated to the minimum extent necessary so that these Terms of Use shall otherwise remain in full force and effect.
      </p>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <h2 id="contact">13. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about these Terms of Use, please contact us:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> legal@topbestllcservice.com</li>
        <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="/contact/">topbestllcservice.com/contact</a></li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Footer notice -->
      <hr class="my-10" />
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        &copy; {siteConfig.currentYear} {siteConfig.name}. Operated by {siteConfig.operator}. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
